descriptionNullable:
### Context
Since hiking is my favorite hobby I oftentimes encounter litter in nature. I decided to take some photos of it and some photos of (mostly) forest floor, because I thought that it might be a nice task to find out whether such a photo contains litter or not.


### Content
Photos of differing quality, from differing angles and distance of forest floor / forest floor with litter on it.

### Baseline
the short demo run on https://github.com/MilanKalkenings/datasets leads to
accuracy 0.9006 (train) 0.8571 (test).
title: Litter on forest floor
subtitle: image classification
